<p>I want to set <strong>minimum</strong> and <strong>maximum</strong> <strong>Pinch-In</strong> and <strong>Pinch-Out</strong> Zoomming Level For MKMapview. so user not Pinch after specific Level Of MKMapview Zooming.Currently I am using <strong>MKMapView+ZoomLevel</strong> Category Class to restrict Zoom-In and Out effect of MapView.</p>  <p>Code:- </p>  <pre><code>- (void)mapView:(MKMapView *)mapView regionDidChangeAnimated:(BOOL)animated {   if([self.mapView zoomLevel]&lt;17) {    CLLocationCoordinate2D centerCoord = {latitude, longitude};         [self.mapView setCenterCoordinate:centerCoord zoomLevel:17 animated:NO]; } }   </code></pre>